{"tid":1795891,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"#hehe#全港sales已經出盡力推銷","createTime":"2019-12-24T08:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T16:30:03.000Z","uid":37330,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"630b8432aae3c7d5cf0659f5f5e9857ecdf7ac68","tid":1795891,"uid":37330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"折折折 %off<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n半年了,大家都抗爭咗半年了<br />\n香港無銷售入口稅嫁<br />\n以前買嘅咁貴全部都俾曬班業主炒家明白 大家都攰了<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你還記得過去係點撐過來的嗎</span></strong></span><br />\n一個一個task <br />\n100百萬遊行  200百萬 狗屋  7.1 流水 10.1<br />\n人權法 中大 理大... <br />\n我地都係一個一個撐過來的<br />\n和平 街頭 極權政府依舊一意孤行<br />\n我地最後嘅一個手段 就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">$$</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">經濟</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">$$</span></span><br />\n12月聖誕係開心嘅節日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n短暫嘅休息係可以<br />\n但可唔可以唔好 見折 就狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見優惠就 買買買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>(香港無銷售入口稅嫁<br />\n以前買嘅咁貴全部都俾曬班業主炒家)</del><br />\n呢幾日嘅商場, 人頭湧湧,大包細包<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以減少不必要嘅開支呀！！！<br />\n做埋啲個罷買task可以嗎？<br />\n坐監 被消失 被自殺,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地係咪唔記得曬啦?!<br />\n班仆街<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍商家</span>、<span style=\"color: navy;\">地產佬</span>, <br />\n就係等緊呢鋪牌翻身呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">醒吓啦</span><br />\n減少非必要開支 減少在港消費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n施加經濟壓力 <br />\n和理非 係我都可以做到的<br />\n最後希望大家買嘢購物前 <br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">停一停 想一想</span></span>"},{"pid":"c67c99a4c1f042d2f58b211699d03c711087eb45","tid":1795891,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:51:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d41b1580a2605d0b2a736c46d1d028af6d275ed","tid":1795891,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"見到仲咁多人買野 真係好灰"},{"pid":"9dfe76f3993f0011317db7beed3ae2b9bfba829f","tid":1795891,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"推多下"},{"pid":"b4328dc3f7c83e1592a3522ca4e7aec66ea7c33b","tid":1795891,"uid":37330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6d41b1580a2605d0b2a736c46d1d028af6d275ed","tid":1795891,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"見到仲咁多人買野 真係好灰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:53:48.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月證明 香港人係有愛 <br />\n,但缺點係太善忘記"},{"pid":"3ee65e55fd8f79a047f57ad7f8898fae683266ad","tid":1795891,"uid":37330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得有啲post,比起底狗post更有意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92804db5e6ab85b402a464e6643050535000dc6","tid":1795891,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:57:38.000Z","msg":"不灰心<br />\n不分化<br />\n不上當<br />\nWe connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae03659d14f3f56859f9a668c51f870054776db","tid":1795891,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply